        "content": "## **How It Works**\n\n1. **Hourly Cron Trigger** â€“ Starts the workflow every hour to fetch updated billing data.\n2. **AWS Billing Fetch** â€“ Retrieves latest cost and usage data via AWS Cost Explorer API.\n3. **Azure Billing Fetch** â€“ Retrieves subscription cost data from Azure Cost Management API.\n4. **GCP Billing Fetch** â€“ Retrieves project-level spend data using GCP Cloud Billing API.\n5. **Data Parser** â€“ Combines and cleans data from all three clouds into a unified format.\n6. **Cost Spike Detector** â€“ Identifies unusual spending patterns or budget overruns.\n7. **Owner Identifier** â€“ Matches resources to their respective owners or teams.\n8. **Auto-Tag Resource** â€“ Tags the affected resource for quick identification and follow-up.\n9. **Alert Sender** â€“ Sends notifications through Email, WhatsApp, and Slack with detailed cost reports."
